hrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-success/15 text-success" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield-check size-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg></span><div><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2"><span class="font-medium text-sm">Administrator Privileges</span><span class="rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 font-medium text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide bg-primary/15 text-primary">Required</span></div><p class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Required to install system packages and modify system configurations</p><p class="mt-2 rounded-md border border-border bg-secondary/50 p-2 font-mono text-muted-foreground text-xs">You will be prompted for your password when needed</p></div></div><div class="shrink-0 self-start sm:self-center"><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium text-success text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check size-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg>Granted</span></div></li></ul><p class="mt-5 text-muted-foreground/70 text-xs leading-relaxed">Administrator privileges are requested with a password prompt only when a change needs them. Full Disk Access is optional but recommended for the smoothest experience.</p></div></div></div></main></div></div><div class="flex shrink-0 flex-col border-border border-t"><div class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-2 text-muted-foreground text-xs transition-colors hover:bg-mut